{"title":"Fork Scallops, Split Post, Swoopy Bars make a Wilder & Faster Hope x Lotus HB.T Track Bike!","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2023-hope-x-lotus-hb-t-next-gen-track-bike/","date":1690821719000,"content":"<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_teaser.jpg\" alt=\"2023 Hope x Lotus HB.T next-gen custom 3d-printed ti &amp; carbon aero track bike for UCI Worlds Glasgow, teaser\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_teaser.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_teaser-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_teaser-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_teaser-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_teaser-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_teaser-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_teaser-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>UCI Worlds are around the corner in Glasgow, and a new generation of the Hope x Lotus HB.T carbon &amp; 3D-printed titanium track bike promises to make British Cycling faster than ever. The HB.T was already wildly – and widely – innovative with its uniquely splayed-out fork legs and seatstays, but it’s even wilder-still in 2023 with new scalloped fork blades, a bent &amp; split aero seatpost, and several new customized swooping carbon bars for sprint &amp; pursuit racing…</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>2023 Hope x Lotus HB.T carbon track bike</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_Team-GB-on-velodrome.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_Team-GB-on-velodrome.jpg\" alt=\"2023 Hope x Lotus HB.T next-gen custom 3d-printed ti &amp; carbon aero track bike for UCI Worlds Glasgow, Tem GB training in velodrome\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_Team-GB-on-velodrome.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_Team-GB-on-velodrome-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_Team-GB-on-velodrome-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_Team-GB-on-velodrome-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_Team-GB-on-velodrome-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_Team-GB-on-velodrome-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_Team-GB-on-velodrome-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a><figcaption><em>c. British Cycling, all photos by <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/swpix_cycling/\" target=\"_blank\">SWPix</a></em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The UCI Cycling World Championships kick off this week in Scotland, and we’re starting to see more new track bike tech than we’ve seen in a while. And that essentially boils down to the fact that any company looking to race new bikes or components in next summer’s Paris 2024 Olympics have been informed by the UCI that they must be raced this summer at Worlds in order to be eligible to race next summer in Paris. So some national teams have been scrambling with their equipment partners to get next-gen track bikes ready, with the Olympics on the line.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>According to British Cycling, “<em>The 2023 UCI Cycling World Championships will see 64 pieces of kit and equipment in total homologated for the Great Britain Cycling Team for potential use at the 2024 Paris Olympic Games</em>“, including bike and clothing.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix-overall.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix-overall.jpg\" alt=\"2023 Hope x Lotus HB.T next-gen custom 3d-printed ti &amp; carbon aero track bike for UCI Worlds Glasgow, angled\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix-overall.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix-overall-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix-overall-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix-overall-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix-overall-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix-overall-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>On the track bike update, that includes a new version of the Hope x Lotus HB.T track bike where the wide-set frame appears mostly unchanged <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/hope-hb-t-x-lotus-3d-printed-ti-carbon-track-bike-is-british-cyclings-wild-olympic-secret-weapon/\" target=\"_blank\">since it was ridden by Team GB</a> to the highest tally of medals at the 2020 Tokyo Olympics, albeit with some apparent seatstay and headtube refinements. But it gets an all-new fork, and all-new seatpost, and at least a couple of new handlebars, as well.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>What’s new?</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_split-seatpost.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_split-seatpost.jpg\" alt=\"2023 Hope x Lotus HB.T next-gen custom 3d-printed ti &amp; carbon aero track bike for UCI Worlds Glasgow, split seatpost\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_split-seatpost.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_split-seatpost-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_split-seatpost-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_split-seatpost-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_split-seatpost-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_split-seatpost-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_split-seatpost-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Let’s start with new split aerodynamic seatpost since that was the first that caught our attention – adorned with the name Renishaw, the additive manufacturing company behind the track bike’s 3D-printed elements. With a new kinked and hollow shape, it somehow reminds me of the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/new-2023-trek-madone-slr-aero-road-bike/\" target=\"_blank\">new Madone</a>, even if it’s almost an opposite design. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_Twin-Seat-Post-detail.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_Twin-Seat-Post-detail.jpg\" alt=\"2023 Hope x Lotus HB.T next-gen custom 3d-printed ti &amp; carbon aero track bike for UCI Worlds Glasgow, split Twin Seat Post\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_Twin-Seat-Post-detail.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_Twin-Seat-Post-detail-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_Twin-Seat-Post-detail-800x600.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_Twin-Seat-Post-detail-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_Twin-Seat-Post-detail-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_Twin-Seat-Post-detail-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>But the idea is similar to the bike’s wide stays – let smooth air move unrestricted in the middle, and move turbulent airflow out near the rider’s spinning legs.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_new-fork-detail.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1350\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_new-fork-detail.jpg\" alt=\"2023 Hope x Lotus HB.T next-gen custom 3d-printed ti &amp; carbon aero track bike for UCI Worlds Glasgow, new scalloped fork\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_new-fork-detail.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_new-fork-detail-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_new-fork-detail-800x600.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_new-fork-detail-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_new-fork-detail-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_new-fork-detail-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Even more interesting though, might be the reshaped fork where the entire trailing edge of the fork legs now get biomimicry-inspired scallops designed to smooth and extend laminar airflow off the fork by moving the air’s separation point further back on the airfoil shape. Interestingly, it looks like the scallops extend both in carbon &amp; 3D-printed titanium off the entire rear length of the fork and its crown.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_new-fork-ends.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_new-fork-ends.jpg\" alt=\"2023 Hope x Lotus HB.T next-gen custom 3d-printed ti &amp; carbon aero track bike for UCI Worlds Glasgow, new dropouts\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_new-fork-ends.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_new-fork-ends-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_new-fork-ends-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_new-fork-ends-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_new-fork-ends-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_new-fork-ends-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_new-fork-ends-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new fork also has a much cleaner curve at its lowest point, now curving its carbon legs down just to meet the axle, with the bolt-on axle now more smoothly integrated in an arc at the hub.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_sprint-bar-detail.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_sprint-bar-detail.jpg\" alt=\"2023 Hope x Lotus HB.T next-gen custom 3d-printed ti &amp; carbon aero track bike for UCI Worlds Glasgow, sprint bar\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_sprint-bar-detail.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_sprint-bar-detail-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_sprint-bar-detail-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_sprint-bar-detail-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_sprint-bar-detail-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_sprint-bar-detail-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_sprint-bar-detail-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Up top, a new sprint dropbar curves forward and up out of its integrated stem to meet grips for the rider, with no traditional crossbar for the handlebar. Again, it appears that the bar is a single piece that includes the upper extensions of the fork legs, the top crown of the fork, the stem, and the bars themselves.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_pursuit-bar-detail.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_pursuit-bar-detail.jpg\" alt=\"2023 Hope x Lotus HB.T next-gen custom 3d-printed ti &amp; carbon aero track bike for UCI Worlds Glasgow, pursuit bar\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_pursuit-bar-detail.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_pursuit-bar-detail-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_pursuit-bar-detail-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_pursuit-bar-detail-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_pursuit-bar-detail-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_pursuit-bar-detail-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>There is also a less dramatically-shaped pursuit base bar, onto which custom risers &amp; extensions are made to fit each athlete. While the base bar is painted black and appears to be made of some 3D-printed metal, various photos of different Team GB pursuit bar setups could suggest either 3D-printed ti or carbon for different racers.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Hope x Lotus HB.T – Pricing, options &amp; availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_buy-now.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_buy-now.jpg\" alt=\"2023 Hope x Lotus HB.T next-gen custom 3d-printed ti &amp; carbon aero track bike for UCI Worlds Glasgow, complete\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_buy-now.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_buy-now-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_buy-now-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_buy-now-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_buy-now-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_buy-now-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-Hope-Lotus-HB-T-updated-custom-aero-3d-printed-titanium-carbon-track-bike_Paris-Olympics-prototype-photo-by-SWPix_buy-now-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Another iteration of the Hope x Lotus HB.T carbon track bike is here, and it is still made-in-the-UK, and still a bike you can actually buy… if you have the budget. The standard frameset sells for £25,000 +VAT in either a pursuit, omnium, or sprint setup. Adding either the new “Twin Seat Post” or the new ” Standard Lotus 3D printed fork” will add another £2000 each, plus tax. Hope disc and a tri-spoke front wheel are also available for £5200-5400 for a set.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.hopetech.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>HopeTech.com</em></a> &amp; <em><a href=\"http://www.britishcycling.org.uk\" target=\"_blank\">BritishCycling.org.uk</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2023-hope-x-lotus-hb-t-next-gen-track-bike/\">Fork Scallops, Split Post, Swoopy Bars make a Wilder &amp; Faster Hope x Lotus HB.T Track Bike!</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"f03f5b082d891eae567dfdb5668f75f52e29ed11891a8d7b30ddd02de2282f95","category":"Cycling"}